{"tid":114724,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本地區PS4與PS3同期銷量對比（截止2016年12月）","createTime":"2017-02-10T04:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T02:27:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ae8fc467efc89e2538f33844a034dc2cced22c","tid":114724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"2017/02/10 08:51<br />\n日本家用機零售市場在逐年萎縮，普遍認為索尼主機PS4的銷量比起上世代嚴重下滑，然而，實際情況真的是這樣嗎？著名網站VGChartz根據日本每周的MC銷量報告繪制了目前PS4與同時期PS3的銷量差距對比圖（截止至2016年12月）：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.vgchartz.com/articles_media/images/december-2016-sales-8-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vgchartz.com%2Farticles_media%2Fimages%2Fdecember-2016-sales-8-1.png&h=84cffc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中縱坐標表示兩台主機同期的銷量差距，正軸表示PS4領先，負軸表示PS3領先，可以看出，儘管在PS4上市後的兩年半的時間內同期銷量不如PS3，但在今年下半年開始，PS4在日本的銷量有著顯著的提升，目前已經超過PS3同期銷量且勢頭強勁。<br />\n<br />\n兩台主機同期總銷量走勢圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.vgchartz.com/articles_media/images/december-2016-sales-7-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vgchartz.com%2Farticles_media%2Fimages%2Fdecember-2016-sales-7-2.png&h=fb4ba012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截止2016年12月，日本市場PS4銷量為406萬9578台，同期PS3銷量為368萬0120台。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://www.vgchartz.com/article/267384/ps4-vs-ps3-in-japanvgchartz-gap-chartsdecember-2016-update/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vgchartz.com%2Farticle%2F267384%2Fps4-vs-ps3-in-japanvgchartz-gap-chartsdecember-2016-update%2F&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=479f8777\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vgchartz.com/article/267384/ps4-vs-ps3-in-japanvgchartz-gap-chartsdecember-2016-update/</a>"},{"pid":"506b86b5d2f6a9093d0aed7b0e488f722d58c799","tid":114724,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"點解仲有人買ps3?<br />\n<br />\n利申唔打機"},{"pid":"6d6ae74b24649cabe3136ea6444093ad8fa14014","tid":114724